description: RAD PDF is a PDF reader, editor, form filler, signer and more for ASP.NET Core, the ASP.NET Framework (3.5/4.x), and ASP.NET 5+, complete with API (client and server) and GUI compatible with almost any web browser. For documentation, please see https://www.radpdf.com/
releaseNotes:
For copyright notice, documentation, sample code using this package, and the RAD PDF System Service, please install https://www.radpdf.com/install/

NOTES:
  If using the default Lite storage provider, RAD PDF will require access to a RAD PDF System Service instance.
  If using SQL Server or a custom Lite storage provider has been implemented, set UseService=false to enable page rendering directly by the DLL and without the System Service.

Sample code can also be cloned from https://github.com/radpdf/samples

More information about releases at https://www.radpdf.com/releases/
